{"tid":449130,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASUS 證實Z270都用到8700k，但Intel表明唔接受","createTime":"2017-10-27T02:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T07:37:23.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2af833c62d0757457a59c66aa33130705771e7c","tid":449130,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=110&amp;tid=2405518&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2Fforum%2Fviewthread.php%3Ffid%3D110%26tid%3D2405518%26page%3D1&d=18JzV%2BojnVE0pgzis5M2DNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=58a2b428\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=110&amp;tid=2405518&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"33f4b867a6d9843940dac6fe65454fd2b45ec6d1","tid":449130,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"bit-tech的編輯在上個星期對華碩ROG主板經理Andrew Wu進行了採訪，後者在採訪中提及了Z270理論上可以支援Coffee Lake處理器，只是Z270在供電上與Z370有一點差異，不過這種供電差異不足以成為一種限制。而目前還有另一種說法，Z370的設計初衷是為了支援將來主流平台的8核處理器，也就是說Z370是專門為Coffee Lake而造的折中產物，為了保證Z370銷量不得不這樣做。<br />\n<br />\nASUS證實Z270平台也可與Intel Coffee Lake CPU相容，但是Intel不同意👎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"149f7110354f875f8f40e4696f434fc447c24e28","tid":449130,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"之前曾經報導Z270和Z370的供電針腳不同，有20個未被使用的針腳被重新設計，其中大部分針腳用於VSS和VCC供電，Intel官方表示Coffee Lake的穩定性要優於上一代，而且超頻能力也得到加強。<br />\n<br />\n不過Andrew Wu還提到，如果Intel允許，主機板廠商可以對管理引擎（Management Engine）和BIOS升級從而無縫相容Coffee Lake。這在一定程度上說明Z270不支援Coffee Lake與設計無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，更多的原因是一個市場策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為Andrew Wu認為已經在使用Z270平台的用戶不會為第八代平台而升級。將Coffee Lake綁定Z370銷售對Intel和主機板廠商來說都是利大於弊，只是讓消費者的額外支出增多了。"},{"pid":"f34bd9f0ef711ffae490bd967c14dd1f25867ab8","tid":449130,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"ASUS 好大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f72c3e3d2e481c67823facbfdf91851c0b5a996","tid":449130,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:39:24.000Z","msg":"shut up and take my money"},{"pid":"430d432d9c6c4e702e647b90cd3b760463a9907a","tid":449130,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"唔接受係乜柒statement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9341d535226eefa905e828dd5f72a96b794be6b","tid":449130,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"咁有無人買8700K照用番Z270而且用到"},{"pid":"5aba147d909ad882bc73249119e6ee3e58d89fc8","tid":449130,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有無人買8700K照用番Z270而且用到</blockquote><br />\n不過Andrew Wu還提到，如果Intel允許，主機板廠商可以對管理引擎（Management Engine）和BIOS升級從而無縫相容Coffee Lake。這在一定程度上說明Z270不支援Coffee Lake與設計無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，更多的原因是一個市場策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為Andrew Wu認為已經在使用Z270平台的用戶不會為第八代平台而升級。將Coffee Lake綁定Z370銷售對Intel和主機板廠商來說都是利大於弊，只是讓消費者的額外支出增多了。"},{"pid":"1df5e49dd1d7cfaa9682cffa7cdd721409bba556","tid":449130,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有無人買8700K照用番Z270而且用到</blockquote><br />\n不過Andrew Wu還提到，如果Intel允許，主機板廠商可以對管理引擎（Management Engi